    Risk protection arrangement for academies: membership rules
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The rules governing the risk protection arrangement (RPA) for academies. 
  </p>

