<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>These are the full risk protection arrangement (<abbr title="risk protection arrangement">RPA</abbr>) rules, including details of your cover.</p>

<p>There’s a separate version for church academies, so make sure you read the right one.</p>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p><a rel="external" href="http://www.education.gov.uk/rpa-optin-form">Join the risk protection arrangement</a></p>
</div>

</div>
